data.description: 5 Private Acres Nestled in Upper Toutle Valley. Drive the Scenic Spirit Lake Hwy adjacent Silver Lake & North Fork of Toutle River, 18 Miles East of I5, Exit 49 Castle Rock. Home & Acreage are off Private shared drive. 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, 1782 sq.ft., 2002 Manufactured Home w/Vaulted Ceilings, 2 Living Rooms, Kitchen w/Island, Dining Space w/Slider to Backyard, Utility Room off Kitchen w/Pantry Shelves, XXXL Primary Suite w/Sitting Room, Deck, Primary Suite w/Step in Shower & Soaker Tub. Other 3 Bedrooms at Opposite end of Home. All bedrooms w/Large Closets. Multiple Outbuildings, the Largest w/New LED Lighting, Concrete Floor & Woodstove. Acreage has accommodated Horse in past.Creek & Pond on Property.Home abuts Ridge w/territorial views.
